      • id

        public Object id()
        Description copied from interface: TitanElement
        Returns a unique identifier for this entity.

        The unique identifier may only be set when the transaction in which entity is created commits. Some entities are never assigned a unique identifier if they depend on a parent entity.

        Titan allocates blocks of identifiers and automatically assigns identifiers to elements automatically be default. This behavior can be partially overridden by setting GraphDatabaseConfiguration.ALLOW_SETTING_VERTEX_ID

        Specified by:
